                            <comment id="12545749" author="jimk" created="Tue, 27 Nov 2007 08:25:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The javadoc error was introduced in another commit and is not related to this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12545750" author="jimk" created="Tue, 27 Nov 2007 08:27:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;javadoc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; /export/home/hudson/hudson/jobs/Hadoop-Patch/workspace/trunk/src/contrib/hbase/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hbase/shell/CreateCommand.java:77: warning - @param argument &quot;table&quot; is not a parameter name.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12545752" author="jimk" created="Tue, 27 Nov 2007 08:37:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Comitted.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12545820" author="hudson" created="Tue, 27 Nov 2007 13:15:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Hadoop-Nightly #315 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://lucene.zones.apache.org:8080/hudson/job/Hadoop-Nightly/315/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://lucene.zones.apache.org:8080/hudson/job/Hadoop-Nightly/315/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12546041" author="jimk" created="Tue, 27 Nov 2007 23:01:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reopening issue. HTable constructor must retry even if table does not exist, because the table may not have been reassigned yet. However, previously the find retried hbase.client.retries.number * hbase.client.retries.number times, instead of just hbase.client.retries.number times.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12546382" author="jimk" created="Wed, 28 Nov 2007 20:42:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed by latest commit for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-249&quot; title=&quot;[hbase] address regression&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-249&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-2276&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12546670" author="hudson" created="Thu, 29 Nov 2007 11:39:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Hadoop-Nightly #317 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://lucene.zones.apache.org:8080/hudson/job/Hadoop-Nightly/317/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://lucene.zones.apache.org:8080/hudson/job/Hadoop-Nightly/317/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
